records.addlTxt:
01:34 PM  Attorney Dan Tombasco appeared for the State. Defendant, Brice E. Rogers, appeared with Attorney Christopher William Rose.  Clerk N. Nobile.
MINUTES: 22CM435/22CM1116. Victim rights compliance. The State moves to dismiss Case 22CM435 for reasons set forth on the record. The State will be reissuing charges and requests Case 22CM1116 be set for the new case when it is filed. Court will scheduled Case 22CM1116 for a status hearing about 3 rotations out to allow the DA's Office enough time to file the new criminal complaint and enough time for a preliminary hearing to be held.  Status conference scheduled for October 31, 2022 at 10:00 am.
